{"tid":2140330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那請巴勒斯坦支持國安惡法，以色列Cellbrite即停電話破解軟件比香港","createTime":"2020-08-05T02:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T19:25:29.000Z","uid":51271,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6b04ecfd74bd002e6d795a6accc0b21522618324","tid":2140330,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T02:34:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/627043070780363/posts/2291030167714970/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F627043070780363%2Fposts%2F2291030167714970%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeaskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=dc7f9fbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/627043070780363/posts/2291030167714970/</a><br />\n<br />\n【🈲成功施壓｜以色列科技公司不再向香港出售手機破解產品 保護手足私隱】<br />\n<br />\n以色列公司Cellebrite是黑警早前招標購買八款手機破解軟件的其中一間，用以解鎖及復原已刪除對話。早前我發起聯署要求公司停止向黑警出售相關技術，以保障手足私隱，結果Cellebrite回覆記者查詢時強調公司不會向被美國制裁的國家或地區出口其產品（而香港是其中一個受美國FATF制裁地區），意味民間壓力成功阻截香港黑警一個破解手機的技術。<br />\n<br />\n是次成功有賴公民社會互相合作，透過輿論迫令企業表態。在我發起聯署後，以色列當地人權組織馬上響應，立即去信國防部、經濟部及Cellebrite，要求當局承諾禁止出口。或者因為《國安法》罪名模糊不清，黑警國安毋需搜查令即可沒收疑犯電子儀器，與國際標準相去甚遠，因此Cellebrite迅速回應外界質疑，暗示與黑警「劃清界線」。<br />\n<br />\n根據招標文件，尚有幾間供應商或會在黑警的要求下提供破解軟件，日後我必會致力跟進，要求相關公司及國家停止助紂為虐助，避免協助中共打壓香港人。<br />\n<br />\n✅以色列Cellebrite InField Ultimate Software<br />\n❓美國F-Response TACTICAL Edition<br />\n❓美國AXIOM Magnet<br />\n❓瑞典MSAB XRY<br />\n❓加拿大EnCase Forensic<br />\n❓英國Blackrainbow Software<br />\n<br />\n報道<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/.premium-human-rights-activists-urge-israel-to-stop-spy-tool-exports-to-hong-kong-police-1.9027488\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2F.premium-human-rights-activists-urge-israel-to-stop-spy-tool-exports-to-hong-kong-police-1.9027488&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeaskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=4185063b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/.premium-human-rights-activists-urge-israel-to-stop-spy-tool-exports-to-hong-kong-police-1.9027488</a><br />\n<br />\n👉訂閱「國際戰線頻道」 零時差緊貼最新動態：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKinternationalfront\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKinternationalfront&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeaskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=87190ea6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKinternationalfront</a>"},{"pid":"5b2e6e4bed3b30568dbbdcf61f113c1a254c072e","tid":2140330,"uid":254183,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T02:36:10.000Z","msg":"反猶先鋒沙田YOU有何感想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8dc4443552181027a76dba96b25351354bde68","tid":2140330,"uid":127929,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T02:41:03.000Z","msg":"原來施壓真係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前仲有人串話以色列親中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6cf4756663dd7c295733f0e63e32b638d701aa","tid":2140330,"uid":105976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T02:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72eff42ec3747873c1acd430f0d441245302359","tid":2140330,"uid":3149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T02:45:19.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b73afac43aadc243c1804d266d0e3a9bee702b6","tid":2140330,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci